	The second  Jewel of the Triple Crown, the Preakness, is running this weekend 
at  Pimlico. Betanything started accepting  horse wagers by telephone at 
800-582-5881 before the Kentucky Derby.  This service has been well received 
by our customers. If you can't get  to the track this weekend, call us and 
place a wager and enjoy the race  on TV. The rules and payouts are listed in 
the Rules and Regulations  section of our site.
	
	Get your racing  form at http://www.racingform.com.
	
	Betanything  continues to offer PGA golf matchups on both Saturday and 
Sunday. NASCAR  odds and spreads are available for the Busch series and the 
Winston Cup  series.
	
	The NBA  playoffs are getting into full swing. If you haven't got on board 
yet,  jump on.
	
	Betanything  continues to offer 15% bonus on all Western Union and Neteller  
deposits.
	
	Good luck to  everyone and have a wonderful weekend!
	
	
